setAverageCPUTimeAndNumOfKeyCmp(StatisticalResults[]) - Method in class InsertionVersusMerge.StatisticalResults
This method sets the average number of key comparisons and CPU Time for the sorting of randomly-ordered arrays by 1) taking in an ArrayList of Results sorted base on CPU Time (sorted using quickSort()) 2) removing the top and bottom 25% of results 3) finding the average of the middle portion (remaining 50%) 4) setting cpuTime to the average found This average is also known as interquartile mean.
setCPUTime(long) - Method in class InsertionVersusMerge.StatisticalResults
 
setNumOfKeyCmp(long) - Method in class InsertionVersusMerge.StatisticalResults
 
StatisticalResults - Class in InsertionVersusMerge
